1. Welcome page links to classes index page and studios index page X
2. Class Index page has list of user's(teacher) yoga classes by day that link to the yoga class show page /yoga_classes
3. Users(teachers) can add new yoga classes /yoga_classes/new *note: can select from existing studio or make a new studio (nested form)
4. User's/teacher's yoga class show page /yoga_classes/:id *note: "add student" button
5. User/Teacher can add student to given yoga class /yoga_classes/:yoga_class_id/student/new 
6. User's/teacher's yoga class show page /yoga_classes/:id *note: "add student" button
7. Index page has list of user's(teacher) studios that link to the studio show page /studios 
8. User's/teacher's studio show page with their classes at that studio /studios/:studio_id/classes (nested route to index) (classes index = classes controller)